'''2011年歐洲超級盃'''（{{lang|en|'''2011 UEFA Super Cup'''}}）是[[歐洲足球協會聯盟|歐洲足協]]舉辦的第36屆[[歐洲超級盃|歐洲超級盃]]賽事，由[[2010/11賽季歐洲冠軍聯賽|2010/11賽季歐洲冠軍聯賽]]冠軍[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞隆拿]]和[[2010/11賽季歐洲聯賽|2010/11賽季歐洲聯賽]]冠軍[[波尔图足球俱乐部|波圖]]對決<ref name=intro>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefasupercup/news/newsid=1640498.html|title=Barcelona and Porto to contest Super Cup|publisher=UEFA.com|date=2011-05-29|language=en|access-date=2011-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110817140016/http://www.uefa.com/uefasupercup/news/newsid=1640498.html|archive-date=2011-08-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>，賽事於2011年8月26日[[摩納哥|摩納哥]][[路易二世体育场|路易二世体育场]]上演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefasupercup/news/newsid=1655727.html|title=Monaco schedule announced|publisher=UEFA.com|date=2011-08-03|language=en|access-date=2011-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111124105857/http://www.uefa.com/uefasupercup/news/newsid=1655727.html|archive-date=2011-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终，巴塞罗那以2–0的比分擊敗波圖，歷史上第4次获得歐洲超級盃冠军<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://soccernet.espn.go.com/report/_/id/331104?cc=5739|title=Cesc seals Super Cup win for Barca|date=2011-08-26|work=ESPN Soccernet|language=en|accessdate=2018-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102061807/http://soccernet.espn.go.com/report/_/id/331104?cc=5739|archive-date=2012-11-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2011/aug/26/cesc-fabregas-barcelona-porto|title=Cesc Fábregas scores first Barcelona goal in Uefa Super Cup triumph|date=2011-08-26|work=Guardian|accessdate=2018-07-26|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810144421/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2011/aug/26/cesc-fabregas-barcelona-porto|archive-date=2017-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

